{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"By the end of this year,"},{"time":2000,"text":"there'll be nearly a billion people on this planet"},{"time":5000,"text":"that actively use social networking sites."},{"time":7000,"text":"The one thing that all of them have in common"},{"time":9000,"text":"is that they're going to die."},{"time":12000,"text":"While that might be a somewhat morbid thought,"},{"time":15000,"text":"I think it has some really profound implications"},{"time":17000,"text":"that are worth exploring."}]},{"cues":[{"time":19000,"text":"What first got me thinking about this"},{"time":22000,"text":"was a blog post authored earlier this year by Derek K. Miller,"},{"time":25000,"text":"who was a science and technology journalist"},{"time":28000,"text":"who died of cancer."},{"time":30000,"text":"And what Miller did was have his family and friends write a post"},{"time":33000,"text":"that went out shortly after he died."},{"time":35000,"text":"Here's what he wrote in starting that out."},{"time":37000,"text":"He said, \"Here it is. I'm dead,"},{"time":39000,"text":"and this is my last post to my blog."},{"time":41000,"text":"In advance, I asked that once my body finally shut down"},{"time":44000,"text":"from the punishments of my cancer,"},{"time":46000,"text":"then my family and friends publish this prepared message I wrote --"},{"time":49000,"text":"the first part of the process"},{"time":51000,"text":"of turning this from an active website to an archive.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":54000,"text":"Now, while as a journalist,"},{"time":56000,"text":"Miller's archive may have been better written"},{"time":58000,"text":"and more carefully curated than most,"},{"time":60000,"text":"the fact of the matter is that all of us today"},{"time":62000,"text":"are creating an archive"},{"time":64000,"text":"that's something completely different"},{"time":66000,"text":"than anything that's been created"},{"time":68000,"text":"by any previous generation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":70000,"text":"Consider a few stats for a moment."},{"time":72000,"text":"Right now there are 48 hours of video"},{"time":74000,"text":"being uploaded to YouTube every single minute."},{"time":77000,"text":"There are 200 million Tweets being posted every day."},{"time":81000,"text":"And the average Facebook user"},{"time":84000,"text":"is creating 90 pieces of content each month."},{"time":88000,"text":"So when you think about your parents or your grandparents,"},{"time":91000,"text":"at best they may have created"},{"time":93000,"text":"some photos or home videos,"},{"time":95000,"text":"or a diary that lives in a box somewhere."},{"time":98000,"text":"But today we're all creating this incredibly rich digital archive"},{"time":101000,"text":"that's going to live in the cloud indefinitely,"},{"time":103000,"text":"years after we're gone."},{"time":105000,"text":"And I think that's going to create some incredibly intriguing opportunities"},{"time":108000,"text":"for technologists."}]},{"cues":[{"time":110000,"text":"Now to be clear, I'm a journalist and not a technologist,"},{"time":112000,"text":"so what I'd like to do briefly"},{"time":114000,"text":"is paint a picture"},{"time":116000,"text":"of what the present and the future are going to look like."},{"time":119000,"text":"Now we're already seeing some services"},{"time":121000,"text":"that are designed to let us decide"},{"time":123000,"text":"what happens to our online profile and our social media accounts"},{"time":126000,"text":"after we die."},{"time":128000,"text":"One of them actually, fittingly enough,"},{"time":130000,"text":"found me when I checked into a deli"},{"time":132000,"text":"at a restaurant in New York"},{"time":134000,"text":"on foursquare."}]},{"cues":[{"time":137000,"text":"(Recording) Adam Ostrow: Hello."},{"time":139000,"text":"Death: Adam?"},{"time":141000,"text":"AO: Yeah."},{"time":143000,"text":"Death: Death can catch you anywhere, anytime,"},{"time":146000,"text":"even at the Organic."},{"time":149000,"text":"AO: Who is this?"},{"time":151000,"text":"Death: Go to ifidie.net"},{"time":154000,"text":"before it's too late."}]},{"cues":[{"time":156000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":158000,"text":"Adam Ostrow: Kind of creepy, right?"},{"time":160000,"text":"So what that service does, quite simply,"},{"time":162000,"text":"is let you create a message or a video"},{"time":164000,"text":"that can be posted to Facebook after you die."},{"time":167000,"text":"Another service right now"},{"time":169000,"text":"is called 1,000 Memories."},{"time":171000,"text":"And what this lets you do is create an online tribute to your loved ones,"},{"time":173000,"text":"complete with photos and videos and stories"},{"time":176000,"text":"that they can post after you die."},{"time":179000,"text":"But what I think comes next is far more interesting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":182000,"text":"Now a lot of you are probably familiar with Deb Roy"},{"time":185000,"text":"who, back in March,"},{"time":187000,"text":"demonstrated how he was able to analyze more than 90,000 hours of home video."},{"time":191000,"text":"I think as machines' ability"},{"time":193000,"text":"to understand human language and process vast amounts of data"},{"time":195000,"text":"continues to improve,"},{"time":197000,"text":"it's going to become possible"},{"time":199000,"text":"to analyze an entire life's worth of content --"},{"time":201000,"text":"the Tweets, the photos, the videos, the blog posts --"},{"time":204000,"text":"that we're producing in such massive numbers."},{"time":206000,"text":"And I think as that happens,"},{"time":208000,"text":"it's going to become possible for our digital personas"},{"time":211000,"text":"to continue to interact in the real world long after we're gone"},{"time":214000,"text":"thanks to the vastness of the amount of content we're creating"},{"time":217000,"text":"and technology's ability to make sense of it all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":220000,"text":"Now we're already starting to see some experiments here."},{"time":223000,"text":"One service called My Next Tweet"},{"time":225000,"text":"analyzes your entire Twitter stream, everything you've posted onto Twitter,"},{"time":228000,"text":"to make some predictions as to what you might say next."},{"time":231000,"text":"Well right now, as you can see,"},{"time":233000,"text":"the results can be somewhat comical."},{"time":235000,"text":"You can imagine what something like this might look like"},{"time":237000,"text":"five, 10 or 20 years from now"},{"time":239000,"text":"as our technical capabilities improve."},{"time":242000,"text":"Taking it a step further,"},{"time":244000,"text":"MIT's media lab is working on robots"},{"time":246000,"text":"that can interact more like humans."},{"time":249000,"text":"But what if those robots were able to interact"},{"time":251000,"text":"based on the unique characteristics of a specific person"},{"time":254000,"text":"based on the hundreds of thousands of pieces of content"},{"time":256000,"text":"that person produces in their lifetime?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":259000,"text":"Finally, think back to this famous scene"},{"time":261000,"text":"from election night 2008"},{"time":263000,"text":"back in the United States,"},{"time":265000,"text":"where CNN beamed a live hologram"},{"time":267000,"text":"of hip hop artist will.i.am into their studio"},{"time":269000,"text":"for an interview with Anderson Cooper."},{"time":272000,"text":"What if we were able to use that same type of technology"},{"time":274000,"text":"to beam a representation of our loved ones into our living rooms --"},{"time":278000,"text":"interacting in a very lifelike way"},{"time":280000,"text":"based on all the content they created while they were alive?"},{"time":283000,"text":"I think that's going to become completely possible"},{"time":286000,"text":"as the amount of data we're producing"},{"time":288000,"text":"and technology's ability to understand it"},{"time":290000,"text":"both expand exponentially."},{"time":293000,"text":"Now in closing, I think what we all need to be thinking about"},{"time":295000,"text":"is if we want that to become our reality --"},{"time":297000,"text":"and if so,"},{"time":299000,"text":"what it means for a definition of life and everything that comes after it."},{"time":302000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":304000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}